I can see some situations where someone might think they were helping you out, for example...<br>
<br>
Player_A tells you: &quot;You've died like 9 times in the past 10 minutes, why don't you come join our group, we could use you.&quot;<br>
<br>
Not saying it happens like that very often...just what I was thinking when I posted my earlier response (because I've had someone send me a tell very similar to that, If I remember correctly I decided to go work on my pottery skills instead).<br>
